{"tid":959790,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本最可愛高中生揭曉！「女子高生Misscon 2018」","createTime":"2018-12-29T01:16:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-29T05:51:00.000Z","uid":25345,"like":3,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"3a0cfdde09d9c344ae0aa2e55cd472cbb280defd","tid":959790,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T01:16:37.000Z","msg":"日本最可愛高中生揭曉！「女子高生Misscon 2018」選美決賽於26日在東京舉行，佐賀縣的高中3年級生亞怜（あれん）從8人中脫穎而出，最終奪得冠軍寶座。<br />\n檢視相片<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/bB8FqNEFD8HoaCt1l9hJVA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTEwO2g9MzAw/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/setn.com.tw/a2ba4194f32a9737ab17634c291037b6\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FbB8FqNEFD8HoaCt1l9hJVA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTEwO2g9MzAw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Fsetn.com.tw%2Fa2ba4194f32a9737ab17634c291037b6&h=da03af00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/099yPnYDNwwQWQbH_Fghbw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTEwO2g9MzYy/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/setn.com.tw/21f971dca78dc48273bc13f9f89ed981\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F099yPnYDNwwQWQbH_Fghbw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTEwO2g9MzYy%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Fsetn.com.tw%2F21f971dca78dc48273bc13f9f89ed981&h=2b4c8a64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲日本最可愛高中生冠軍亞怜。（圖／翻攝自《modelpress》）<br />\n根據日本《Modelpress》報導，今年的參賽者分別來自日本6個地區，包括「關東」、「關西」、「九州‧沖繩」、「北海道‧東北」、「中部」以及「中國‧四國」，據了解，這場選美比賽從2015年開始舉辦，至今已經是4屆了，一開始會先從日本全國各地區選出8人，接著再與上屆比賽的冠軍刑部結生一同進入決賽較勁。<br />\n檢視相片<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/z0E71iKlmThvNlvnkUrrOQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTEwO2g9MzYw/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/setn.com.tw/d0ea7f99c60b0e74cf8a67dbe757afd0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fz0E71iKlmThvNlvnkUrrOQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTEwO2g9MzYw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Fsetn.com.tw%2Fd0ea7f99c60b0e74cf8a67dbe757afd0&h=12146472&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲亞怜打敗日本全國各地的選手。（圖／翻攝自《modelpress》）<br />\n<br />\n最終決賽的名單於26日公布，奪得冠軍的是佐賀縣的高中3年級生亞怜（あれん），她獲獎後感動表示，「對於許多人的支持和鼓勵，我由衷地謝謝大家」。而亞軍則是石川縣的高中3年級生美雲（みゆん)，今年是她第2次參賽。<br />\n<br />\n不過部分網友似乎不認同比賽結果，紛紛留言直呼，「我覺得亞軍比較像冠軍」、「真正可愛的都沒入選」、「素質普普。」（編輯：鄭餘蓉）<br />\n檢視相片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/9f0nkDug6HjSZSu9x5aOFw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTEwO2g9MzYz/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/setn.com.tw/374f73fae353f8ff33245f63aa56bd26\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F9f0nkDug6HjSZSu9x5aOFw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTEwO2g9MzYz%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Fsetn.com.tw%2F374f73fae353f8ff33245f63aa56bd26&h=c4c4d1cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲亞軍美雲。（圖／翻攝自《modelpress》）<br />\n檢視相片<br />\n<br />\n▼▲進入決賽的8名女高中生。（圖／翻攝自《modelpress》）"},{"pid":"083aaa6fa5b1209b617ebff8864b004e11c3df55","tid":959790,"uid":40348,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T01:19:27.000Z","msg":"Mk妹屌打晒佢地啦"},{"pid":"2c14c729a2a6e2dd239944242a6a025738abf0c1","tid":959790,"uid":77355,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T01:20:08.000Z","msg":"。。。。屁股下巴"},{"pid":"efce75fc3592a0fddbbc1ca9825f7a95771710a2","tid":959790,"uid":79077,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T01:23:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"598c14b5eccdb48a9fe12c012fcf5bb53f252fc5","tid":959790,"uid":82450,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T01:28:19.000Z","msg":"北海道<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c41ad242b8aeee2791f97cd483cdd021babe1e9","tid":959790,"uid":215401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T0